	<h1 class="title">又有 5 座城市被联合国授予「设计之都」称号</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-12-03 08:39:07 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/4044/medium/4044.jpg?1436644589" alt="" />			
	</div>
